These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, almond-milk
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, potato, cabbage
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles, filmmaking
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, pilot, security-guard
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, blues, disco
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, russian, nigerian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, baseball, handball
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the russian##1
 2. the person who's sport is handball is the security-guard##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is between the nigerian and the person drinking sprite##2
 4. the fan of blues is on the left of the japanese##1
 5. the pilot is the person eating cabbage##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the japanese##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | sprite    | almond-milk   | iced-tea           |
| Food          | potato       | cabbage    | pomegranate         |
| Hobby         | puzzles    | filmmaking  | cooking        |
| Job           | project-manager | pilot   | security-guard      |
| Music-Genre   | blues        | disco    | r&b       |
| Nationality   | russian     | japanese  | nigerian       |
| Sport         | ice-hockey     | baseball | handball |

