.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, cola, milk
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, asparagus, lime
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, drama, fantasy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, r&b, soul
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, turkish, thai
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, guinea-pig
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, volleyball, soccer
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the turkish##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking water##2
 5. the thai is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking cola is the fan of salsa##1
 7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 8. the person eating eggplant is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the fan of soul##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | water   | milk    | cola         |
| Food          | eggplant    | asparagus | lime          |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | fantasy  | drama     |
| Music-Genre   | soul       | r&b      | salsa         |
| Nationality   | thai      | turkish   | polish    |
| Pet           | goldfish        | guinea-pig      | hamster         |
| Sport         | volleyball | snowboarding  | soccer |

