The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, baking, chess
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, martial-arts, disaster
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, blues, techno
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, german, argentine
3 different pets are kept: snake, turtle, lizard
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, surfing, handball
 1. the person eating pomegranate is the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the argentine is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is the person eating cucumber##1
 4. the person watching martial-arts movies is the owner of the turtle##1
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is between the german and the fan of techno##2
 8. the german is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
10. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
11. the german is the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Food          | cucumber      | pomegranate      | raspberry      |
| Hobby         | woodworking   | chess | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | martial-arts    | disaster          |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | disco      | techno          |
| Nationality   | german    | pakistani  | argentine      |
| Pet           | snake   | turtle  | lizard        |
| Sport         | skiing  | surfing   | handball     |

