The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, animation, spy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, dubstep, classical
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, turkish, french
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit, turtle
 1. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is the french##1
 3. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 5. the fan of techno is between the person watching animation movies and the person drinking fanta##2
 6. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the fan of techno is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the doctor is the owner of the turtle##1
 9. the person drinking water is between the doctor and the fisherman##2
10. the french is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Beverage      | fanta | water           | hot-chocolate      |
| Hobby         | singing       | skydiving         | baking       |
| Job           | doctor    | photographer | fisherman |
