3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, goldfish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, cricket
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller
 1. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the fan of country##2
 6. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who's sport is baseball and the owner of the goldfish##2
 7. the person driving the helicopter is between the person eating pumpkin and the person drinking cola##2
 8. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 9. the freelancer is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
10. the doctor is the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
