 5. the person driving the train is on the right of the thai##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 7. the person driving the ship is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the indian##2
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 9. the person watching mystery movies is the person driving the train##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
11. the person driving the train is the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | iced-tea      | coffee      |
| Hobby         | cooking     | chess     | rock-climbing  |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | drama  | mystery |
| Nationality   | french  | thai     | indian |
| Pet           | chinchilla        | goldfish | rabbit     |
| Sport         | baseball    | weightlifting | basketball   |
| Transport     | airplane        | ship        | train   |

