.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, 7up
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, pear, strawberry
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, skydiving, rock-climbing
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, photographer, journalist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, teasy, documentary
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, weightlifting, golf
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, van
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the journalist##1
2. the person driving the van is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person eating pear is on the left of the dancer##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person watching thriller movies and the photographer##2
5. the person eating strawberry is between the journalist and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
9. the person watching teasy movies is on the left of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
