.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, lemonade
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, cauliflower, carrot
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, entrepreneur, videographer
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, australian, pakistani
3 different pets are kept: ferret, cat, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, volleyball, snowboarding
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, trike
1. the person drinking coffee is the person eating carrot##1
2. the person driving the trike is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the analyst is between the person drinking lemonade and the owner of the rat##2
4. the egyptian is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
7. the entrepreneur is the person eating pomegranate##1
8. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
9. the australian is between the person eating pomegranate and the person driving the bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | fanta    | coffee       | lemonade      |
| Food          | pomegranate   | carrot   | cauliflower  |
| Job           | entrepreneur  | analyst | videographer    |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | australian     | pakistani  |
| Pet           | rat     | ferret        | cat |
| Sport         | volleyball | weightlifting   | snowboarding  |
| Transport     | helicopter    | trike     | bike      |

 